Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:25.49,CQ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be3}遠く歌う海よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:31.15,CQ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be3}出会った二人の未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:34.93,CQ1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be3}永遠に誓って
